*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+ REQUIREMENTS +*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*
	Server / ISP:
		- Linux oder MacosX, (NO Windows!)
		- Apache HTTP Server (or similar, must support .htaccess) => http://httpd.apache.org/download.cgi
		- PHP >= 4.4 => http://www.php.net/downloads.php (no CGI Installation recommended)
           + Imap Library + Mysql + GD-Lib
           (Tellmatic is developed and tested under PHP 4.4.7 and latest PHP5 stable releases + suhosin)
		- Mysql Datenbank >= v4.1 (Mysql 4.1.x/5, NO Mysql3!)
           (Tellmatic is developed and tested under latest Mysql 4.x and latest Mysql5 stable releases)
		- Access to SMTP, POP3/IMAP Server
		- Optional: Cronjobs, PHP CLI or wget (Cronjobs execute at least every 5 Min.)
    
    Client:   
       standard Browser with Javascript support (Seamonkey, Mozilla or Firefox, IE (limited, no 24Bit PNG support))



*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+ BASIC-FEATURES V1.0.x +*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*
	Eaysy installation, installed in 2 minutes
	Comfortable and intuitive web frontend
	Multiuser
	Online help
	Multilingual
	Filemanager
	Different styles for frontend
	Wysiwyg Online-Editor (TinyMCE) & spellchecker	
	Blacklist (blacklist by email, domain or regular expression)
	Multiple mailservers for SMTP and POP3/IMAP (maildelivery and bouncemanagement)
	Graphical statistics
	Geographical maps (subscriptions, readers, etc.), using GeoIP API and database
	Scheduled mail delivery, (with cronjobs), write now, send in two weeks
	Multiple address-/recipientgroups per address (private and public groups, define default groups/subcribers can choose from public groups etc)
	Newslettergroups
	Bouncemanagement
	Errormanagement, delivery-errors, address-errors etc
	General statistics and reports
	"Clean Up Database"-Feature (delete, move failed addresses etc)
	Email-Reports 
	Click-/Linktracker
	Viewtracker (blank blindimage, or any other png/jpg)
	Email validation (3 levels for internal and subscriptions)
	CSV address import
	CSV address export
	Personalized newsletter (add a private salutation etc, track clicks, views etc.)
	Massmailing (send anonymized newsletter)
	Delivery via SMTP
	Double opt-in/out
	Subscription-form-generator
	Unlimited attachments
	

